{"tid":827304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女爛醉無力反抗　3男當街撿屍影片瘋傳","createTime":"2018-09-18T23:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T04:49:23.000Z","uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c236a571b763490709f3686c00b039579688957","tid":827304,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T23:43:56.000Z","msg":"這樣太危險！酒後撿屍社會新聞頻傳，但仍有不少女生戒心不足，近日社群網路又在瘋傳一段影片，一名香港正妹疑似喝太多失去意識，最後被3名男子半扛半拖拉上計程車、內褲都不見了，網友看完不禁搖頭嘆息，「這劇情我看過......。」<br />\n<br />\n根據影片內容，這名酒醉正妹中間一度嘗試反抗掙脫，但沒有成功，黑色外衣男子一直叫不到車還氣得連罵髒話，有網友注意到片中的男生下體疑似出現生理反應，懷疑3人動機不單純，但最後女主角有無平安回家、影片本身沒有交代。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180919/1432365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180919%2F1432365&d=9siJFAaRUHZW6EtVwHtQSl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=99ccda09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180919%2F1432365&h=9616c01b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180919/1432365</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180919/640_c24af8b436549875dc9fed336bac3d6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180919%2F640_c24af8b436549875dc9fed336bac3d6f.jpg&h=ab8f58d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過多幾年，連登仔埋單，不怕"},{"pid":"17390c0d1a85e44b209b9fca28c3d5234373bacc","tid":827304,"uid":44454,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T23:50:22.000Z","msg":"唔好次次都講瘋傳好唔好，都唔知瘋左去邊？"},{"pid":"f5baa2d8abb26010f77b1fd49028d8986bdd294b","tid":827304,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T23:52:20.000Z","msg":"潮爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de43402c0def7f8ff08fae19ec0dfd7cb79618cd","tid":827304,"uid":117302,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"17390c0d1a85e44b209b9fca28c3d5234373bacc","tid":82730